I still could not disentangle my thoughts, but Audace came to myrescue.

"To conclude," he said (and an audible ouf! was emitted by cruelLouise), "our patient's trouble concerns not a certain physical act but theimagining of its performance. All he can do in his mind is omit theswiveling part altogether and shif